# Build-time configured single origin the shell will trust as its parent
# window (used for postMessage origin filtering). Bake this into the build
# before deploying — Vite inlines import.meta.env.* at build time, so it
# CANNOT be changed at runtime.
#
# Dev fallback (when unset) is "*" which is permissive — never ship a
# build with this unset to production.
VITE_PARENT_ORIGIN=https://your-parent-app-origin.example
